t5291.text: Nonbinary does not mean “half woman,”. It doesn’t even mean “10% woman”. Gender is a complicated thing — it’s not a gradient where one end is male and the other is female, with nonbinary smack bang in the middle. Some of us are both but some of us are also neither.
